家架 持久戰end乜game<br />\n依一刻 我地未贏過 亦都冇野輪 得林奠想end咋<br />\n同我保撚住自己手足 香港需要你地！"},{"pid":"47ae43908822b2edf098056b93360aaed4791fa8","tid":1519793,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:03:42.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0sv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=c95e8be7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0sv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=a05ede4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0sv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=575e338e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike